T02TD2819E:169b-0: @169b * // 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs rdo rje'i rgyas btab pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2819E:169b-1: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs la dad pa thob pas /
T02TD2819E:169b-3: gdon gyis glags btsal ba dang /
T02TD2819E:169b-4: rkun po dang dgras 'jigs pa'i nus pa'i dbang ba bsrung ba la sogs pa'i don du snying rje chen pos srung skud bcing bar bya'o //
T02TD2819E:169b-5: 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen dang //
T02TD2819E:169b-6: padmo sna tshogs kha dog can //
T02TD2819E:169b-7: ras dang dar dang bal dang bcas //
T02TD2819E:170a-2: gzhon nu gos dmar gos dkar gyon //
T02TD2819E:170a-3: rgyan dmar rgyan dkar de bzhin du //
T02TD2819E:170a-4: cod pan thabs dang shes rab 'dzin //
T02TD2819E:170a-6: mchod pa kun sngon 'gro ba yis //
T02TD2819E:170a-8: gnyis kyis srad bu bzhag nas ni //
T02TD2819E:170a-9: bgegs bsal gtor ma sngon song sbyar //
T02TD2819E:170a-10: de rjes lhag pa'i lhar bskyed nas //
T02TD2819E:170a-12: srad bu bsnams pas dgyes bzhugs la //
T02TD2819E:170a-14: lus ngag sems gsum bcings pa yi //
T02TD2819E:170a-15: rgya gsum phyag rgya bsam pa ste //
T02TD2819E:170a-16: ting nge 'dzin gsum sngags gsum rim //
T02TD2819E:170a-17: slob dpon mi g-yeng la gnas pas //
T02TD2819E:170a-18: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis bcings dang //
T02TD2819E:170a-19: sdigs mdzub rdo rje rtse gcig nyid //
T02TD2819E:170a-20: sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD2819E:170a-21: 'od phyung rdo rje'i rgyas btab pa'o //
T02TD2819E:170a-22: aom a'a:hr'i:k'a ya badzra k'a ya kantha h'um /
T02TD2819E:170a-23: aom a'a:hr'i:w'aka badzra w'aka kantha h'um /
T02TD2819E:170a-24: aom a'a:hr'i:tsitta badzra tsatti kantha h'um /
T02TD2819E:170a-25: dam tshig srad bu dung dang byi ru gser 'od beed'ura aindra'i mdog gsal ba //
T02TD2819E:170a-26: rgya gsum 'bar ba'i rdo rje sku gsung thugs dag skal ldan lus ngag yid btab pa //
T02TD2819E:170a-27: slob dpon mthu chen po ta la yi 'phags pa sras mchog snying rjes shin tu non pa'i yid //
T02TD2819E:170a-28: ting 'dzin lcags kyus de nyid bcug la gus pa bzang ldan mgul dang dpung pa bcing ;
T02TD2819E:170a-29: / srung skud kyi cho ga rdzogs so//
